OL,5, The rate of corporation tax, paid on   
OL,6, company profits, will rise next month, 
OL,7, the chancellor has confirmed.          
OL,9,FIt will go up from 19% to 25% for      
OL,10,Fcompanies with over #250,000 in        
OL,11,Fprofits, Jeremy Hunt told the Commons. 
OL,13,FHe also announced a new scheme to allow
OL,14,Fevery pound invested by businesses in  
OL,15,FIT equipment, plants or machinery to be
OL,16,Fdeducted in full from taxable profits. 
OL,18,FThe tax hike, first announced in 2021  
OL,19,Fwhen Rishi Sunak was chancellor, has   
OL,20,Fbeen a source of much political debate.
